OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDr Aaron Beck: Cognitive   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbehavioural therapy pioneer
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdies aged 100              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Dr Aaron Beck, an American psychiatrist
OL,6, considered the father of cognitive     
OL,7, behavioural therapy, has died aged 100.
OL,9,FCBT, which was originally developed to 
OL,10,Fmanage depression, aims to help change 
OL,11,Fthe way people think to improve how    
OL,12,Fthey feel and alter their behaviour.   
OL,14,FDr Beck's work is considered hugely    
OL,15,Finfluential. He published hundreds of  
OL,16,Farticles and 25 books in his career.   
OL,18,FA statement from his daughter said he  
OL,19,Fhad "transformed the field of mental   
OL,20,Fhealth" with his life's work.          
